{"title":"Silca Asks: Wax vs Oil?","link":"https://theradavist.com/silca-asks-wax-vs-oil/","date":1726062363000,"content":"<p>Wax vs Oil: Which is the better chain lube?</p>\n<p>Josh from Silca is here to answer one of the more asked questions about SILCA recently. If <a href=\"https://silca.cc/products/chain-waxing-system?_pos=5&amp;_sid=d3330b2f8&amp;_ss=r\" target=\"_blank\">hot melt chain waxing</a> is the way of the future for drivetrain lubrication then why does SILCA make <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9c3967ea-9801-442a-9d09-419007ae71c3&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsilca.cc%2Fproducts%2Fsynergetic-wet-lube%3F_pos%3D1%26_sid%3Ddbac5a3c3%26_ss%3Dr\" target=\"_blank\">Synergetic</a> and <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=9c3967ea-9801-442a-9d09-419007ae71c3&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fsilca.cc%2Fproducts%2Fsynerg-e-e-bike-lube%3F_pos%3D2%26_sid%3Dd3cf7581b%26_ss%3Dr\" target=\"_blank\">Synerg-E oil</a> based lubricants?</p>\n<p>We’re curious if you’ve tried hot wax yet? If so, does it <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/silca-chain-waxing-system-review/\" target=\"_blank\">live up to the hype</a>?</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/silca-asks-wax-vs-oil/\">Silca Asks: Wax vs Oil?</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"c726e2280abb033132366b6a21fb36f82511bb7c09e75d56b58f5034a9f81d27","category":"Cycling"}